data.chText: 不知疲劳的；孜孜不倦的；坚持不懈的
data.enText: continuing to do sth for a long period of time with a lot of effort and/or enthusiasm

tr: characterized by hard work and perseverance

value.def: If you describe a person or their efforts as untiring, you approve of them because they continue what they are doing without slowing down or stopping.

example.ex: ...an untiring fighter for justice, democracy and tolerance.
example.tran: 为公正、民主和宽容奋斗不息的斗士
